queries.queryString:
_sourceCategory=<proofpoint source>
| json field=_raw "spamScore"
| json field=_raw "malwareScore"
| json field=_raw "phishScore"
| json field=_raw "impostorScore"
| if(spamScore != 0, 1, 0) as spam_num
| if(malwareScore != 0, 1, 0) as malware_num
| if(phishScore != 0, 1, 0) as phish_num
| if(impostorScore != 0, 1, 0) as impostor_num
| timeslice 1h
| sum(spam_num) as spam, sum(malware_num) as malware, sum(phish_num) as phish, sum(impostor_num) as impostor by _timeslice

_sourceCategory=<proofpoint source>
| json field=_raw "spamScore"
| if(spamScore != 0, 1, 0) as spam_num
| sum(spam_num) as spam, count(_messages) as messages
| (spam / messages) * 100 as spam_pct
| fields - spam, messages

_sourceCategory=<proofpoint source>
| json field=_raw "impostorScore"
| if(impostorScore != 0, 1, 0) as impostor_num
| sum(impostor_num) as impostor, count(_messages) as messages
| (impostor / messages) * 100 as impostor_pct
| fields - impostor, messages

_sourceCategory=<proofpoint source>
| json field=_raw "phishScore"
| if(phishScore != 0, 1, 0) as phish_num
| sum(phish_num) as phish, count(_messages) as messages
| (phish / messages) * 100 as phish_pct
| fields - phish, messages

_sourceCategory=<proofpoint source>
| json field=_raw "malwareScore"
| if(malwareScore != 0, 1, 0) as malware_num
| sum(malware_num) as malware, count(_messages) as messages
| (malware / messages) * 100 as malware_pct
| fields - malware, messages

_sourceCategory=<proofpoint source>
| json field=_raw "senderIP"
| json field=_raw "sender"
| json field=_raw "recipient"
| json field=_raw "quarantineFolder"
| json field=_raw "spamScore"
| json field=_raw "malwareScore"
| json field=_raw "phishScore"
| json field=_raw "impostorScore"
| where !(spamScore = 0) or !(malwareScore = 0) or !(phishScore = 0) or !(impostorScore = 0)
| count by sender, senderIP, recipient, quarantineFolder, spamScore, malwareScore, phishScore, impostorScore
| sort by _count desc
